## IsExtends type

if A extends B (no distributed condition type), return true, else return false.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export type IsExtends<A, B> = [A] extends [B] ? true : false
```

## Example


```ts
 // Expect: true
 type Foo = IsExtends<1, number>
```
